displayName.text: Dr Steven Joseph Caldroney, DDS MD

formattedAddress: 423 E 23rd St, New York, NY 10010, USA
adrFormatAddress: 423 E 23rd St, New York, NY 10010, USA

originalText.text: Dr. Caldroney really made me feel at ease when I had two wisdom teeth pulled in 2014. He has a wonderful bedside manner and an appropriate sense of humor. The office was cozy, clean, and not crowded. I really felt attended to by the young woman at the front desk. I recall his office had state of the art equipment for x-rays and the equipment to put me under as I was too afraid to stay awake for the procedure. I remember being able to take my time waking up and not feeling pushed out of the door. Excellent office, reception, and service. This practice was a MetLife participant and the claim went through smoothly. I would definitely return although I hope I never have to for obvious reasons.
